#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"See the [[<span class=\"application\">Gpg4win</span> documentation on\n"
"verifying signatures|http://www.gpg4win.org/doc/en/gpg4win-compendium_24.html#id4]].\n"
